Dear Obuj Mon,
After availing a club card, you will receive 20 points every month if you spend at least Tk. 2000. For every additional Tk. 1000 spending, you will receive additional 10 points. After your points total reaches 250, you can redeem the points for the first time. The points can be redeemed as price discount. 1 point= Tk. 1 price discount.
You need to do at least 2000 taka worth of shopping every month to have your loyalty points added to your main point balance. Once you reach 250 points, you can start redeeming 1 taka for 1 point collected.
Thank you.
